?BMessages|messages||Messages
?Toverview
$BXTrkCad$ generates three types of messages:

$BNotices$, which appear in their own window and require you to press a button 
to make a choice or dismiss them.

$BError messages$, which appear in the $XStatus Bar|statusBar$ and 
are accompanied by a beep.

