?LI
$Gdbox$ $Gdfilbox$ $BBoxes$ and $BFilled Boxes$ are created by selecting one corner and dragging the opposite corner.
A $BBox$ is composed of four lines which may be individually deleted.
?LI
$Gdpoly$ $Gdfilpoly$ $BPoly Lines$ and $BPolygons$ are created by $BLeft-Dragging$, and a corner is placed when you release the Left mouse button.
The $BPoly$ shape is finished by pressing the $BSpace$ key or by selecting another operation.
