Objects can be changed by the $XModify Command|cmdModify$:
?LSo
?LI
The End-Points of a $BLine$, $BDimension Line$, $BTable Edge$ or $BBenchwork$ can be dragged to new positions.
A $BBox$ is treated as 4 Lines.
?LI
An $BCurved Line$ is modified in same manner as modifying a curved track.
?LI
Selecting a corner of a $BPoly Line$, $BFilled Box$ or $BPolygon$ moves that corner to a new position, and if moved close to a neighboring corner will merge the two corners and delete the edge between them.
Selecting an edge will create a corner that can be dragged to a new position.
